			  	Making military bases does not build ships faster, it only pays for upkeep: which means say a doom costs 10mp per turn and each military base gives 10mp then you can build 1 doom every military base, if you have 1 military base and 2 dooms the money comes out of your PP income because you wouldnt have enough MP to pay for it. which is bad cause mp costs alot of pp.<br />
<br />
To increase ship building speed build lots of factory.<br />
<br />
 look at domestic, upkeep, and Fleet/Ship Upkeep (PP) if fleet/shipupkeep is higher than 0 you need more military bases to make mp to pay for ship upkeep.			   <P align=right></P>
